HOW TO BUY

HOW TO BUY

Create a Wallet

Download MetaMask or your preferred wallet app from the App Store or Google Play Store. If you're using a desktop, install the MetaMask extension via metamask.io.

Get Some ETH

To swap for $LIFEDOG, you'll need ETH in your wallet. If you don't have ETH, you can:

 • Purchase it directly on MetaMask.

 • Transfer ETH from another wallet.

 • Buy ETH on another exchange and send it to your wallet.

Go to Uniswap

Visit app.uniswap.org, connect your wallet and then copy and paste the $LIFEDOG coin address into Uniswap:

Select $LIFEDOG and confirm. When MetaMask prompts you for a signature, sign the transaction.

Swap ETH for $LIFEDOG

Swap your ETH for $LIFEDOG and bring your dead meme coins back to life! Stake them with $LIFEDOG, or stake just $LIFEDOG to harvest rewards in $LIFEDOG.

FAQ

FAQ

What is $LIFEDOG?

-

$LIFEDOG is a meme coin, the king of all meme coins, with an absolutely unique feature—the ability to "resurrect" other meme coins. By staking your meme coins (Ethereum-based for now) together with $LIFEDOG, you can earn staking rewards, giving new life to your tokens while enjoying extra benefits.
